text.tspan: Use followed by any motion to yank (copy).
Use to paste after (if charwise, to the right, if linewise, below).
Text deleted with , , is also copied!
() and an a - z character before any yank/delete/paste command
An A - Z register before yank/delete means append-copy.
enters insert mode in a new empty line below the current one.
does the same above the current line.
